ONIMATA-X1 is a half-oni with special trait & coming to be the next Luden in the group. She's not a leader type and she likes to be left alone.

ONIMATA PROJECT (オニマタ) is a project where I'm going to introduce my oni-friends to the world. ONI means demon in Japanese, and MATA means eye in Bahasa Indonesia.

The very first version of Ultra Rare (UR) ONIMATA Character Card.
